title: Mario Kart 8 Installer - Cemu 1.8.1b
description:
Features                         
                             ▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀                         
                                                               
                    Latest MK8 Update (v64/4.1)                
                                                               
                          Complete MK8 DLC                     
                                                               
        100% Save Game Unlocked Chars/Lvls/Stamps/Karts/Miis   
                                                               
                       Cemu Emulator v1.8.1b                   
                                                               
           Cemuhook Plugin 0.4.2.0 - H264 decoder support      
                                                               
      80% Complete Transferable Shader Cache for Multiple Games
                                                               
               Collection of the Best Graphics Packs           
                                                               
                 Preconfigured Controller Profiles             
                                                               
               keys.txt containing over 400 Title Keys         
                                                               
            Optional VB2012/15 x86/x64 Download & Install      
                                                               
             10 Custom Icons for Cemu & Related Folders        
                                                               
         CemuGUI 1.0.1.4 - Preconfigured CoverFlow Front End   
                                                               
        WiiU USB Helper - For Downloading Games/Updates & DLC  
                                                               
      Built-in Cemu Update Function - The Installer Will Check 
                                                               
     Cemu.info and if a Newer Version is Available You Will Be 
                                                               
                     Prompted to Auto Update                   
                                                               
      Built-in Game Update Function - The Installer Will Check 
                                                               
      Nintendo Servers For Game Updates if a Newer Version is  
                                                               
           Available You Will Be Prompted to Auto Update       
                                                               
      You Can Disable Online Cemu/Game Update Checks By Using  
                                                               
                The Following Switch /OFFLINE=TRUE
